SUMMARY:2026 Kirkland Shamrock Run (5k\, 10k and Lil Leprechaun Run)
DTSTAMP:20260314T153651Z
DTSTART:20260314T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:A Kirkland and Eastside tradition is put on my Running Company\
	, Cascade Stride. This is the run that everyone talks about weeks after th
	e race! Signing up early saves LOTS of money. Come join Lake Washington Ph
	ysical Therapy and Cascade Stride by "wearing the green" for a fun family 
	fun run. The event will start and end at the Marina Park in Kirkland\, WA.
	 Run along Lake Washington Blvd and enjoy views of Lake Washington and the
	 Seattle skyline. Registration fees\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events
	/#/details/2026-kirkland-shamrock-run-5k-10k-and-lil-leprechaun-run/182910
	42/2026-03-14T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
